scene_description_enriched: The scene depicts Saint Sebastian, a young man with a halo, tied to a tree and being shot with arrows by several archers. He is unclothed except for a loincloth and bands around his wrists and legs. A green parrot is perched on a branch of the tree. In the background, a rocky landscape rises towards a distant castle. The overall setting is outdoors, with a suggestion of a natural environment.
